EXTRACTED VALUE: TimeShift has its moments, but you'll wish that you could rewind time and re-release the game with more imaginative level design and smarter AI.
I hope this sells like hotcakes because I would love to see Mistwalker and Artoon deliver a sequel and continue on the series.
This is pure, unadulterated four-wheeled destruction on an epic scale, and I haven't had this much fun playing a racing game in ages.
It is thoroughly enjoyable and easily recommendable, but it doesn't really compare to its PC counterpart.
